01:23.992 --> 01:30.619
Then the first theme was what I was

01:31.392 --> 01:45.594
feeling when I was child, between the war, in a small town, small, very, very small village, surrounded, very thick, dense forest.

01:46.115 --> 01:46.515
Thick.

