10:28.061 --> 10:29.102
Ah, yes.

10:29.122 --> 10:29.242
Yes.

10:29.262 --> 10:30.744
And this is after the birth of your son?

10:31.084 --> 10:33.666
Then... Or prior to the birth of your son?

10:33.686 --> 10:34.147
Yeah, yeah.

10:34.167 --> 10:35.147
I met the birth of my son.

10:35.167 --> 10:38.230
Then I am very deeply troubled and I...

10:38.632 --> 10:44.357
